00:12:13.110 --> 00:12:16.990
I'll get a little coffee and just you know
focus on my stuff and get it done on a break.

00:12:16.990 --> 00:12:19.199
But to use all that
time efficiently while I'm having coffee.

00:12:19.199 --> 00:12:20.279
While I go to
the bathroom.

