you know I'll make sure that I get those pictures

00:12:28.060 --> 00:12:30.100
off
during the day and then reformat the card

00:12:30.100 --> 00:12:31.100
and keep using it.

00:12:31.100 --> 00:12:33.370
At the end of the day, that needs to be done.

00:12:33.370 --> 00:12:35.370
