I keep three fully charged
batteries.

00:12:37.149 --> 00:12:38.819
But the end of the day I'm putting one in.

00:12:38.819 --> 00:12:41.459
It's the last thing I do before I go to bed.

00:12:41.459 --> 00:12:46.040
Make sure
you got a fully charged battery the next morning.

00:12:46.040 --> 00:12:47.629
That's
sort of my routine.

00:12:47.629 --> 00:12:48.629
Every night do that.

00:12:48.629 --> 00:12:49.769
Then you're ready
fresh for the next day.

00:12:49.769 --> 00:12:51.889
Have the bag packed have it
ready for sunrise.

