Sort
of a Burning Man in the City sort of thing.

00:19:48.049 --> 00:19:50.580
I love
shooting people.

00:19:50.580 --> 00:19:57.159
These are all sort of
interesting-looking people that were at this

00:19:57.159 --> 00:19:58.399
thing.

00:19:58.399 --> 00:19:59.799
And
I shoot anything and everything.

00:19:59.799 --> 00:20:02.370
I shoot people, I shoot
landscapes.

00:20:02.370 --> 00:20:03.610
I shoot nature.

00:20:03.610 --> 00:20:04.610
Flowers.

